\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {2}{\ignorespaces Analysis Logic UML Diagram. Depicts the solver pipeline: XMLParser constructs the StructuralModel, GlobalAssembler builds the global stiffness matrix (K) and load vector (F), Solver solves $\mathbf  {K} \mathbf  {D} = \mathbf  {F}$, and PostProcessor extracts and formats results.}}{3}{figure.2}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:analysis_logic}{{2}{3}{Analysis Logic UML Diagram. Depicts the solver pipeline: XMLParser constructs the StructuralModel, GlobalAssembler builds the global stiffness matrix (K) and load vector (F), Solver solves $\mathbf {K} \mathbf {D} = \mathbf {F}$, and PostProcessor extracts and formats results}{figure.2}{}}
