\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3}{\ignorespaces System Architecture Diagram. Illustrates the full software stack with module dependencies: parser.py defines data models, element\_physics.py computes local stiffness and FEF, matrix\_assembly.py assembles global matrices, banded\_solver.py solves the linear system, and post\_processor.py extracts results.}}{4}{figure.3}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:system_architecture}{{3}{4}{System Architecture Diagram. Illustrates the full software stack with module dependencies: parser.py defines data models, element\_physics.py computes local stiffness and FEF, matrix\_assembly.py assembles global matrices, banded\_solver.py solves the linear system, and post\_processor.py extracts results}{figure.3}{}}
