\newlabel{fig:activity_diagram}{{4}{5}{Activity Diagram showing the high-level control flow: Parse XML $\rightarrow $ Assemble global matrices $\rightarrow $ Apply boundary conditions $\rightarrow $ Solve linear system $\rightarrow $ Post-process and output results}{figure.4}{}}
